WITH item_filter AS (
  SELECT i_item_sk, i_product_name, i_manufact
  FROM item
  WHERE i_manufact_id BETWEEN 748 AND 748+40
),
matching_items AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT i1.i_product_name
  FROM item_filter i1
  WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM item i2
    WHERE i2.i_manufact = i1.i_manufact
      AND (
        (i2.i_category = 'Women' AND 
         (i2.i_color = 'gainsboro' OR i2.i_color = 'aquamarine') AND 
         (i2.i_units = 'Ounce' OR i2.i_units = 'Dozen') AND
         (i2.i_size = 'medium' OR i2.i_size = 'economy')
        ) OR
        (i2.i_category = 'Women' AND
         (i2.i_color = 'chiffon' OR i2.i_color = 'violet') AND
         (i2.i_units = 'Ton' OR i2.i_units = 'Pound') AND
         (i2.i_size = 'extra large' OR i2.i_size = 'small')
        ) OR
        (i2.i_category = 'Men' AND
         (i2.i_color = 'chartreuse' OR i2.i_color = 'blue') AND
         (i2.i_units = 'Each' OR i2.i_units = 'Oz') AND
         (i2.i_size = 'N/A' OR i2.i_size = 'large')
        ) OR
        (i2.i_category = 'Men' AND
         (i2.i_color = 'tan' OR i2.i_color = 'dodger') AND
         (i2.i_units = 'Bunch' OR i2.i_units = 'Tsp') AND
         (i2.i_size = 'medium' OR i2.i_size = 'economy')
        ) OR
        (i2.i_category = 'Women' AND 
         (i2.i_color = 'blanched' OR i2.i_color = 'tomato') AND 
         (i2.i_units = 'Tbl' OR i2.i_units = 'Case') AND
         (i2.i_size = 'medium' OR i2.i_size = 'economy')
        ) OR
        (i2.i_category = 'Women' AND
         (i2.i_color = 'almond' OR i2.i_color = 'lime') AND
         (i2.i_units = 'Box' OR i2.i_units = 'Dram') AND
         (i2.i_size = 'extra large' OR i2.i_size = 'small')
        ) OR
        (i2.i_category = 'Men' AND
         (i2.i_color = 'peru' OR i2.i_color = 'saddle') AND
         (i2.i_units = 'Pallet' OR i2.i_units = 'Gram') AND
         (i2.i_size = 'N/A' OR i2.i_size = 'large')
        ) OR
        (i2.i_category = 'Men' AND
         (i2.i_color = 'indian' OR i2.i_color = 'spring') AND
         (i2.i_units = 'Unknown' OR i2.i_units = 'Carton') AND
         (i2.i_size = 'medium' OR i2.i_size = 'economy')
        )
      )
  )
)
SELECT i_product_name
FROM matching_items
ORDER BY i_product_name
LIMIT 100;
